---
title: Crispy Mozzarella-Crusted Chicken with Roasted Broccoli and Buttery Couscous
description: Crispy panko-coated chicken sounded pretty tough to top, but luckily, our chefs were up to the challenge. They went and made it 65x (a scientific number) more delicious by adding mozzarella and Italian Seasoning to the crunchy coating. And while the chicken is the main event, the sides are excellent accompanying acts. We’re serving up savory, buttery couscous and crispy-edged roasted broccoli. The best part, though? Everything comes together in under 40 minutes! Talk about a weeknight win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w32-r4-crispy-mozzarella-crusted-chicken-fe69446f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/crispy-mozzarella-crusted-chicken-5d0a8f4733dd96000a333b56-2ef26b72.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/crispy-mozzarella-crusted-chicken-5d0a8f4733dd96000a333b56
time required: 35 minutes
